  <h5>Convention Halls</h5>
  <p class="card-text">We have wedding halls, party halls, conference halls and convention halls for various events.</p>
  <p class="card-text-link"><small><a class="click" href="/convention">Click here</a> to book a convention hall.</small></p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card" style="max-width: 600px">
<img src="/public/images/room.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
<div class="card-body">
  <h5>Stay</h5>
  <p class="card-text">We have deluxe rooms, standard suites and presidential suites.</p>
  <p class="card-text-link"><small><a class="click" href="#">Click here</a> to book a room.</small></p>
</div>
</div>

